## üìã Dual Licensing Notice

This project uses a **dual-licensing model**:

### üÜì Free Tier (MIT License)
- **Core Components:** Basic UI components and utilities
- **Open Source:** Full access to source code
- **Community Support:** GitHub issues and discussions
- **No Restrictions:** Commercial and personal use allowed

### üí∞ Commercial Tier (Commercial License Required)
- **Premium Features:** Advanced components and enterprise features
- **Commercial License:** Required for production use of premium features
- **Priority Support:** Dedicated support channels
- **White-label Rights:** Available for Enterprise licenses

### üìñ Commercial License Agreement
For commercial use of premium features, please refer to:
**File:** `licenses/COMMERCIAL_LICENSE.md`
**Web:** https://tamyla.com/licensing

### üîç License Validation
The software includes automatic license validation for premium features:
- Free features work without any license
- Premium features require a valid commercial license
- License status is checked at runtime
- Upgrade prompts guide users to commercial licensing

### üìû Contact for Commercial Licensing
